00:39:07,230 --> 00:39:10,210
[foreboding music]

891
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:13,130
♪ ♪

892
00:39:13,130 --> 00:39:15,190
- [grunts]

893
00:39:15,210 --> 00:39:17,190
[hollers]

894
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:24,230
♪ ♪

895
00:39:27,070 --> 00:39:29,170
