910
00:40:50,050 --> 00:40:53,250
If Plover's right,
it should cure Josh.

911
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:56,170
- Monsters in Library!

912
00:40:56,190 --> 00:40:59,230
[tense music]

913
00:40:59,250 --> 00:41:02,190
- Sheila must have sent it.
- Monsters in Library!

914
00:41:02,190 --> 00:41:04,110
- All right, we have to go
before they leave.

915
00:41:04,130 --> 00:41:05,280
- Okay, I'll grab Margo
and the axes.

916
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:07,130
Hey, you sure
this is gonna work?

917
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,130
- Well, either it will,

918
00:41:08,130 --> 00:41:10,150
or when you come back
we'll both be fish.

919
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:13,030
- Well, that'd be
an improvement.

920
00:41:13,050 --> 00:41:17,000
♪ ♪

921
00:41:17,010 --> 00:41:19,170
- Okay.
- Okay.

922
00:41:19,190 --> 00:41:23,090
