00:41:29,010 --> 00:41:32,190
♪ ♪

927
00:41:32,190 --> 00:41:34,280
Ugh.

928
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:37,190
Yeah, I'm totally feeling that.

929
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:39,110
- Okay.
